        // Research Modals

        // Research Modal 1
        #researchModal1.research-modal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='researchModal1Label', aria-hidden='true')
            .modal-dialog.modal-xl(role='document')
                .modal-content
                    button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-label='Close')
                        span(aria-hidden='true')
                            i.fas.fa-times
                    .modal-body.text-center
                        .container
                            .row.justify-content-center
                                .col-lg-8
                                    // Research Modal - Title
                                    h2.research-modal-title.text-secondary.text-uppercase.mb-0#researchModal1Label PhD Project
                                    // Icon Divider
                                    .divider-custom
                                        .divider-custom-line
                                        .divider-custom-icon
                                            i.fas.fa-star
                                        .divider-custom-line
                                    // Research Modal - Text
                                    p.mb-5
                                        | In my PhD project, under the working title “Personalising Document-level Machine Translation for Dialogue”, my supervisors and I strive to address problems related to phenomena in text which are poorly translated by modern MT systems. Specifically, we work on increasing document cohesion in the translated text, as well as incorporate extra-textual information (e.g. speaker gender) into the translation process. We also aim to bring awareness to the community about the importance of document-level evaluation of translation.
                                        | This PhD is realised in partnership with the industry partner ZOO Digital.

                                    button.btn.btn-primary(data-dismiss='modal')
                                        i.fas.fa-times.fa-fw
                                        | Close Window
